      <prop type="x-translation-ref">考槃.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>考槃在澗，碩人之寬，獨寐寤言，永矢弗諼。
考槃在阿，碩人之薖，獨寐寤歌，永矢弗過。
考槃在陸，碩人之軸，獨寐寤宿，永矢弗告。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He has reared his hut by the stream in the valley,
— That large man, so much at his ease.
Alone he sleeps, and wakes, and talks.
He swears he will never forget [his true joy].
He has reared his hut in the bend of the mound,
— That large man, with such an air of indifference.</seg>
      </tuv>
